## Refactor Service to use JSON file

We need data that match our new interface definitions. We refactor our service to read data from a JSON file with the same structure that the interfaces.

I have created some sample data in a json file [here](https://raw.githubusercontent.com/daniru/blog/step_3/src/assets/data/data.json) that contains data exported from the firebase list that we will be using later on. So we can export/import the JSON file to work locally and remotely.  We can copy the file in **assets/data/data.json**. {.alert .alert-info}

