We have two new @Output events in the component, that will emit event when the user click edit or delete options. We inject the authService in the constructor to be able to check permissions in the template.

In the template we have added a button in the top right corner, that will use the material menu to display the edit and delete options for the admin users. The button will be only rendered if the user is administrator.

Remember to add **MdMenuModule** and **MdIconModule** to the blog Module. {.alert .alert-warning }

